					</div>

					<div id="elementor-tab-content-2785" class="elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix" data-tab="5" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="elementor-tab-title-2785"><p>Wood Scientist</p><p>Involved in intensive research pilot study of developing industrial Hemp wood substitutes such as Hemp particle Boards, Hemp MDF boards and Hemp hard wood.</p><p>Involved in the study of bamboo hard wood which he has identified can be combined seamlessly with the Hemp Hurds.</p><p>High lighting industrial Hemps potential:</p><ol><li>Environmental rejuvenation</li><li>Significant input into Kenya achieving its 10% minimum forest cover target</li><li>Hemp Charcoal briquettes</li></ol><p>Live-stream on YouTube channel  <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCjS7sQPyHQG7tCQnagZnK9w" target="_blank" rel="noopener">777Hemperor</a> Time: 02:00 pm.</p></div>
